<item>
            <title>[LUCENE-2080] Improve the documentation of Version</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LUCENE-2080</link>
                <project id="12310110" key="LUCENE">Lucene - Core</project>
                        <description>&lt;p&gt;In my opinion, we should elaborate more on the effects of changing the Version parameter.&lt;br/&gt;
Particularly, changing this value, even if you recompile your code, likely involves reindexing your data.&lt;br/&gt;
I do not think this is adequately clear from the current javadocs.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
            <key id="12441055">LUCENE-2080</key>
            <summary>Improve the documentation of Version</summary>
